{"id":17756,"date":"2021-10-13T17:39:20","date_gmt":"2021-10-13T17:39:20","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/woffice.io\/?p=17756"},"modified":"2021-10-13T17:47:26","modified_gmt":"2021-10-13T17:47:26","slug":"woffice-is-now-a-full-featured-project-management-tool","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/woffice.io\/woffice-is-now-a-full-featured-project-management-tool\/","title":{"rendered":"Woffice is now a Full Featured Project Management Tool"},"content":{"rendered":"<p>We can officially say that, WE DID IT!<\/p>\n<p>We have been working really hard to move towards the needle. In the last quarter, we have focused a lot to deliver, based on our customer needs. Convert Woffice to a full featured platform, that can help you achieve every aspect on your Project Management journey.<\/p>\n<p>Introducing, Project Management Addons!<\/p>\n<h3 class=\"feaure-text-heading\">Kanban boards<\/h3>\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/woffice.io\/downloads\/woffice-kanban\/\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-14640\" src=\"https:\/\/woffice.io\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/kanban-300x193.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"193\" srcset=\"https:\/\/woffice.io\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/kanban-300x193.png 300w, https:\/\/woffice.io\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/kanban.png 356w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" \/><\/a><br \/>\nSee work moving through multiple stages in Kanban board. Empower teams to self-manage with a better understanding of workflows as they get notified of tasks moving from one stage to another.<\/p>\n<h3 class=\"feaure-text-heading\">Timeline \/ Gantt charts<\/h3>\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/woffice.io\/downloads\/woffice-timeline\/\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-17523\" src=\"https:\/\/woffice.io\/wp-content\/uploads\/edd\/2021\/09\/Woffice-Timeline-300x193.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"193\" srcset=\"https:\/\/woffice.io\/wp-content\/uploads\/edd\/2021\/09\/Woffice-Timeline-300x193.png 300w, https:\/\/woffice.io\/wp-content\/uploads\/edd\/2021\/09\/Woffice-Timeline.png 356w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" \/><\/a><br \/>\nUse Timeline View to visualize and plan tasks to stay on your schedule. Set dependencies between tasks and easily adjust your plans as work changes and deadlines shift.<\/p>\n<h3 class=\"feaure-text-heading\">Google Doc Integration<\/h3>\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/woffice.io\/downloads\/docs-to-wiki\/\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-16846\" src=\"https:\/\/woffice.io\/wp-content\/uploads\/edd\/2021\/09\/image3-300x193.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"193\" srcset=\"https:\/\/woffice.io\/wp-content\/uploads\/edd\/2021\/09\/image3-300x193.png 300w, https:\/\/woffice.io\/wp-content\/uploads\/edd\/2021\/09\/image3.png 745w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" \/><\/a><br \/>\nUse your existing Google Docs folders to create a big library of documentation or file management inside Woffice.<\/p>\n<h3 class=\"feaure-text-heading\">Advanced Tasks<\/h3>\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/woffice.io\/downloads\/advanced-tasks-for-woffice\/\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-16929\" src=\"https:\/\/woffice.io\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/09\/image_1-300x191.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"191\" srcset=\"https:\/\/woffice.io\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/09\/image_1-300x191.png 300w, https:\/\/woffice.io\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/09\/image_1-768x488.png 768w, https:\/\/woffice.io\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/09\/image_1.png 975w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" \/><\/a><br \/>\nA more advanced view for your Woffice Interal view, allowing to see in details tasks. A new modern UI interface for this view also.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>We can officially say that, WE DID IT! We have been working really hard to move towards the needle. In the last quarter, we have focused a lot to deliver, based on our customer needs. Convert Woffice to a full [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":3,"featured_media":0,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":[],"categories":[18],"tags":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/woffice.io\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/17756"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/woffice.io\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/woffice.io\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/woffice.io\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/3"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/woffice.io\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=17756"}],"version-history":[{"count":5,"href":"https:\/\/woffice.io\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/17756\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":17759,"href":"https:\/\/woffice.io\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/17756\/revisions\/17759"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/woffice.io\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=17756"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/woffice.io\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=17756"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/woffice.io\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=17756"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}